00:00:03.949 --> 00:00:06.240
How to Climb Mount Everest.

00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:09.490
You may not be able to move mountains, but
they can move you.

00:00:09.490 --> 00:00:13.400
Standing at the top of the world after an
extremely challenging climb can be a profound

00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:14.400
experience.

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:24.310
You will need $60,000 Excellent physical condition
Weights A practice mountain An expedition

00:00:24.310 --> 00:00:33.190
group The proper gear Visualization techniques
Energy Safety practices A mountain-climbing

00:00:33.190 --> 00:00:36.190
